### Hadith 1:258

*Narrated 'Aisha:*

Whenever the Prophet took the bath of Janaba (sexual relation or wet
dream) he asked for the Hilab or some other scent. He used to take it in
his hand, rub it first over the right side of his head and then over the
left and then rub the middle of his head with both hands.

